{"tid":2146152,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"當年500萬買太古城 今日帳面賺500萬離場","createTime":"2020-08-08T11:42:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-08T13:37:25.000Z","uid":166360,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"30a6e8601096bd8debdf5204b57db410a517f794","tid":2146152,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T11:42:06.000Z","msg":"當年500萬買太古城 今日帳面賺500萬離場<br />\n19:05 2020/08/08<br />\n<br />\n&quot;太古城為鳳山閣低層B室單位，單位實用面積約為582平方呎，建築面積約為675平方呎，為兩房間隔，原業主叫價約1,100萬元，議價後減價100萬元，終以1,000萬元易手，折合實用呎價約為17,182元......原業主於2010年3月以約500萬元購入上述物業，是次轉手帳面獲利約500萬元，物業升值100%。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ps.hket.com/article/2718960/%E7%95%B6%E5%B9%B4500%E8%90%AC%E8%B2%B7%E5%A4%AA%E5%8F%A4%E5%9F%8E%20%E4%BB%8A%E6%97%A5%E5%B8%B3%E9%9D%A2%E8%B3%BA500%E8%90%AC%E9%9B%A2%E5%A0%B4?mtc=60037\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fps.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2718960%2F%25E7%2595%25B6%25E5%25B9%25B4500%25E8%2590%25AC%25E8%25B2%25B7%25E5%25A4%25AA%25E5%258F%25A4%25E5%259F%258E%2520%25E4%25BB%258A%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%25B8%25B3%25E9%259D%25A2%25E8%25B3%25BA500%25E8%2590%25AC%25E9%259B%25A2%25E5%25A0%25B4%3Fmtc%3D60037&d=Ieu1u4uPL9fG%2BDPeYXLiW%2F2x0mEA6i1FZlyL0j1bjmE%3D&h=e4a452e7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ps.hket.com/article/2718960/%E7%95%B6%E5%B9%B4500%E8%90%AC%E8%B2%B7%E5%A4%AA%E5%8F%A4%E5%9F%8E%20%E4%BB%8A%E6%97%A5%E5%B8%B3%E9%9D%A2%E8%B3%BA500%E8%90%AC%E9%9B%A2%E5%A0%B4?mtc=60037</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">十年樓價翻一番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"75bb8352372ea522691a59df5171dac09cee03ff","tid":2146152,"uid":262409,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T11:48:54.000Z","msg":"算吾算少？中間又吾租出去⋯⋯"},{"pid":"43b310ef9e7ff281cc44feed9591e0b0e04c54f6","tid":2146152,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"75bb8352372ea522691a59df5171dac09cee03ff","tid":2146152,"uid":262409